\frac{1}{p}+\frac{1}{q}=1
\{z \in \mathbb{R}^d; \forall x \in \mathbb{R}^d: \langle x,z \rangle \leq \|x\|_p\} = \{z \in \mathbb{R}^d; \|z\|_q \leq 1\} 
